Oh, God, please help us!

968
01:39:03,517 --> 01:39:07,419
Jesus, Holy Mary.

969
01:39:07,488 --> 01:39:09,479
Mother of Christ.

970
01:39:09,557 --> 01:39:13,084
Please, help us.

971
01:39:13,160 --> 01:39:16,391
Please, help us.

972
01:39:16,464 --> 01:39:19,126
We're begging.

973
01:39:22,370 --> 01:39:24,770
Please, save us.

974
01:39:29,510 --> 01:39:31,637
Jesus.

975
01:39:33,914 --> 01:39:38,044
Jesus,Jesus, please.

976
01:40:24,865 --> 01:40:28,699
Oh, thank Christ.

977
01:40:36,844 --> 01:40:39,642
Here, take that
back there to the cleat.

978
01:40:44,385 --> 01:40:46,717
What happened?
I'm okay.

979
01:40:46,787 --> 01:40:48,778
You sure?
