980
01:40:48,856 --> 01:40:50,847
Sean's out there.

981
01:40:50,925 --> 01:40:52,859
What?
He wanted to come.

982
01:40:52,927 --> 01:40:55,760
It's okay, wasn't it?
Where are they?

983
01:40:55,830 --> 01:40:59,698
They're in the current,
drifting towards
Cable Junction.

984
01:40:59,767 --> 01:41:03,396
All right, you three
get to the lighthouse
and stay there.

985
01:41:03,471 --> 01:41:05,735
Stay there!
I'm sorry, Dad.
I didn't know.

986
01:41:05,806 --> 01:41:08,707
It's all right. Forget it.
Just get to the lighthouse!

987
01:41:17,485 --> 01:41:21,148
We're almost there.
I don't think
it's gonna work.

988
01:41:21,222 --> 01:41:23,486
Come on, Patrick,
more to port.

989
01:41:23,557 --> 01:41:26,287
We're gonna make it.
Keep turning.
We've got to land on it.

990
01:41:26,360 --> 01:41:28,328
More to port,
goddamn it!

991
01:41:28,396 --> 01:41:30,330
It's all
the way over.
Shit.

992
01:41:30,398 --> 01:41:34,926
Larry, are we going to
make it to the island?

993
01:41:35,002 --> 01:41:37,470
We're steering for it,
kid.

994
01:41:37,538 --> 01:41:40,939
[ Doug ]
Yeah, but the
wind drift is lateral.

995
01:41:41,008 --> 01:41:43,476
- What does that mean?
- We're going sideways.

996
01:41:43,544 --> 01:41:45,842
For every yard
we go that way,
we go that way a yard.

997
01:41:45,913 --> 01:41:47,972
Yeah, but we were
heading right for it.
We don't have it anymore.

998
01:41:48,048 --> 01:41:51,313
Shit!
Shit, shit, shit!

999
01:42:02,663 --> 01:42:04,722
No, wait, wait,
stop paddling.

1000
01:42:04,799 --> 01:42:06,767
What about the island?
The shark!

1001
01:42:14,642 --> 01:42:16,405
[ Indistinct Noise ]
[ Gasping ]

1002
01:42:32,226 --> 01:42:34,160
[ Brooke ]
What's happening?

1003
01:42:34,228 --> 01:42:36,128
[ Andy ]
I don't know,
I think we're stuck.

1004
01:42:36,197 --> 01:42:38,597
I think it's just
the bottom.
Yeah.

1005
01:42:38,666 --> 01:42:41,066
[Jackie ]
It's that thing!
No, no, it's the bottom.

1006
01:42:41,135 --> 01:42:44,571
No, it's not the bottom.
It's that thing.
It's gonna kill us!

1007
01:42:44,638 --> 01:42:46,037
It's gonna kill us now!

1008
01:42:46,106 --> 01:42:49,633
-Jackie, shut up!
- No, it's gonna kill us!

1009
01:42:49,710 --> 01:42:51,644
Shut up!
Larry!

1010
01:42:51,712 --> 01:42:54,340
Leave her alone!
Then you
take care of her!

1011
01:42:54,415 --> 01:42:56,508
Larry, she's hysterical.
Beating her head in--

1012
01:42:56,584 --> 01:42:58,484
Sit down!
Knock it off, Larry!

1013
01:42:58,552 --> 01:43:00,076
Be quiet!

1014
01:43:00,154 --> 01:43:02,918
- [ Yelling ]
- Shut up!

1015
01:43:02,990 --> 01:43:06,426
- Listen!
- She shouldn't freak out!

1016
01:43:06,494 --> 01:43:08,485
[ Lucy ]
Listen!

1017
01:43:08,562 --> 01:43:11,122
You hear it?

1018
01:43:14,702 --> 01:43:17,398
[Jackie Crying ]

1019
01:43:17,471 --> 01:43:22,033
[ Indistinct Noise ]

1020
01:43:22,109 --> 01:43:24,805
Over there!

1021
01:43:24,879 --> 01:43:27,040
It's coming towards us!

1022
01:43:29,750 --> 01:43:31,945
It's Dad!
It's Dad!

1023
01:43:32,019 --> 01:43:36,183
[ Cheering ]

1024
01:43:56,210 --> 01:43:58,508
[ Cheering ]

1025
01:43:58,579 --> 01:44:03,414
Good. I'm getting
off of here. Good.

1026
01:44:03,484 --> 01:44:08,012
[ Cheering ]

1027
01:44:08,088 --> 01:44:12,923
[ Cheering ]

1028
01:44:14,595 --> 01:44:18,725
Home!
We're goin' home!

1029
01:44:20,568 --> 01:44:24,698
Pull yourselves over.
Gonna get the hell outta here.

1030
01:44:24,772 --> 01:44:27,434
We can't.
We're stuck on the bottom.

1031
01:44:27,508 --> 01:44:30,170
I'll get you closer.
You'll come aboard.

1032
01:44:30,244 --> 01:44:32,405
Just move alongside.
Please hurry!

1033
01:44:32,479 --> 01:44:34,538
[ Brody ]
All right,
hold it steady.

1034
01:44:34,615 --> 01:44:36,776
- [ Screaming ]
- Oh, sh--!

1035
01:44:38,452 --> 01:44:40,852
- [ Yelling ]
- [ Screaming ]

1036
01:44:44,491 --> 01:44:47,255
[ Screaming ]

1037
01:44:48,963 --> 01:44:51,158
Wait! No! Wait!

1038
01:44:56,236 --> 01:44:58,568
Dad!

1039
01:45:09,617 --> 01:45:13,883
I'm all right.
Hold on!

1040
01:45:20,594 --> 01:45:22,687
All right, take this!

1041
01:45:22,763 --> 01:45:25,095
I'll try and
get you over.

1042
01:45:29,203 --> 01:45:31,899
All right, tie it on!
Okay!

1043
01:45:42,783 --> 01:45:46,241
All right, pull these hooks
over with the rope.

1044
01:45:46,320 --> 01:45:50,586
Secure them to the raft.
I'll pull you back with
the wench, got it?

1045
01:45:50,658 --> 01:45:52,091
Okay!

1046
01:46:17,584 --> 01:46:20,451
All right,
now pull it over.

1047
01:46:33,267 --> 01:46:35,235
It's stuck!

1048
01:46:35,302 --> 01:46:39,033
Wait a minute.
I'll put it in reverse.

1049
01:46:51,719 --> 01:46:54,051
[ Screaming ]

1050
01:46:56,857 --> 01:46:59,121
[ Screaming ]

1051
01:47:02,029 --> 01:47:05,965
[ Screaming ]

1052
01:47:06,033 --> 01:47:09,059
[ Screaming ]

1053
01:47:10,904 --> 01:47:13,372
[ Muffled Screaming ]

1054
01:47:23,183 --> 01:47:26,380
L-L-Lucy!
Lucy, look out!

1055
01:47:26,453 --> 01:47:29,650
Oh, my God!
No!

1056
01:47:29,723 --> 01:47:31,657
No!

1057
01:47:34,094 --> 01:47:37,359
Lucy! Hold on!

1058
01:47:37,431 --> 01:47:40,559
[ Screaming ]
No!
Lucy!

1059
01:47:44,705 --> 01:47:49,836
No! Oh, my God! No!

1060
01:47:49,910 --> 01:47:52,970
[ Sean ]
Dad! Dad!

1061
01:47:53,046 --> 01:47:54,775
Hold on!

1062
01:47:58,185 --> 01:48:01,621
[Jackie ]
Get away!

1063
01:48:04,298 --> 01:48:08,200
Get away!

1064
01:48:20,548 --> 01:48:24,245
[ Screaming ]
No!
Dad!

1065
01:48:32,627 --> 01:48:37,291
[ Sean ]
Get away! No!

1066
01:48:38,966 --> 01:48:41,696
[ Sobbing ]
