- No-o-o-o-o!
- Sean!

1071
01:49:05,459 --> 01:49:10,226
[ Screaming ]

1072
01:49:10,298 --> 01:49:12,095
No!

1073
01:49:12,166 --> 01:49:14,396
Da-a-a-a-a-d!

1074
01:49:14,468 --> 01:49:19,770
[ Sean ]
Da-a-a-a-d!

1075
01:49:23,077 --> 01:49:25,841
[ Muffled Blows ]

1076
01:50:06,520 --> 01:50:09,546
- Where'd he go?
- Where is he?

1077
01:50:09,623 --> 01:50:14,390
