1086
01:51:09,650 --> 01:51:12,175
Chief! Chief!

1087
01:51:12,253 --> 01:51:16,019
That's it! Attaboy!
Come on!

1088
01:51:16,090 --> 01:51:19,150
[ Brody ]
Right over here!
[ Sean ] Dad!

1089
01:51:19,226 --> 01:51:21,319
