1093
01:51:31,939 --> 01:51:34,430
Come on!

1094
01:51:34,508 --> 01:51:36,373
[ Sean ]
Look out!
[ Brody ]
Come on!

1095
01:51:36,444 --> 01:51:38,878
Come on! Open wide!
Open wide!

1096
01:51:38,946 --> 01:51:41,278
Say ah-h-h-h!
[ Screaming ]

1097
01:51:49,890 --> 01:51:52,518
Oh, my God!

1098
01:51:52,593 --> 01:51:54,925
[ Screaming ]

1099
01:51:56,330 --> 01:51:58,594
[ Screaming ]
Oh, my God!

1100
01:52:11,745 --> 01:52:13,838
[ Andy ]
He got it! He got it!

1101
01:52:36,337 --> 01:52:39,272
Son of a bitch.

1102
01:52:39,340 --> 01:52:43,071
